High-powered human rights lawyer Amal Clooney held a press conference in Washington DC today calling for the release of imprisoned former president of Maldives Mohamed Nasheed .
George Clooney 's newlywed wife appeared before reporters at the National Press Club at 10 am Thursday , accompanied by Laila Ali , the wife of the jailed politician .
Mrs Clooney said she will not rest until Nasheed walks free .